org.gvsig.mapsheets.layout

Class MapSheetsFrameText

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.app.project.documents.layout.fframes.FFrame
      • org.gvsig.app.project.documents.layout.fframes.FFrameText
        • org.gvsig.mapsheets.layout.MapSheetsFrameText
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, IFFrame, IPrintable, IMapSheetsIdentified, Disposable, Observable, Persistent

    public class MapSheetsFrameText
extends FFrameText
implements IMapSheetsIdentified
    Special text frame that keeps a text template with a wildcard. Will be refreshed for each different sheet. Wildcard will be replaced with associated attribute value.
